1. What are at least two reasons someone might want to build their own computer?
    Save money, custom configuration, have fun!
    
2. The video mentions an optical drive. What's your best guess as to what this is?
    An optical drive can read CDs, DVDs, BlueRay discs, etc.
    
3. From where does the hard drive receive power?
    The power supply.
    
4. From where does the hard drive recieve data?
    The motherboard.
    
5. What should appear if all is set up correctly?
    The BIOS screen.
